'''天主教薩凡納教區'''（{{lang-la|Diocesis Savannah}}；{{lang-en|Roman Catholic Diocese of Savannah}}）是[[美國|美國]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]。教區管轄[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]東南部九十個縣，教座位於東部[[薩凡納|薩凡納]]。

教區有超過77200位教友、57個堂區和107名司鐸，面積為37038[[平方英里|平方英里]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=The Roman Catholic Diocese of Savannah |url=https://www.diosav.org/ |publisher=The Roman Catholic Diocese of Savannah |accessdate=2020-03-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305151425/https://www.diosav.org/ |archivedate=2020-03-05 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>現任教區主教為{{link-en|斯德望·D·帕爾克斯|Stephen D. Parkes}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 08.07.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/07/08/200708b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-07-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708161543/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/07/08/200708b.html |archivedate=2020-07-08 |language=en |date=2020-07-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-en|J·基文·博倫德|J. Kevin Boland|若望·基文·博倫德}}<ref>{{cite web |title=The Most Reverend John Kevin Boland, D.D. |url=https://www.diosav.org/our-bishops/bishop-boland |publisher=The Roman Catholic Diocese of Savannah |accessdate=2020-03-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305144059/https://www.diosav.org/our-bishops/bishop-boland |archivedate=2020-03-05 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

教區於1850年7月3日設立，1937年1月5日易名為'''薩凡納-亞特蘭大教區'''，1956年7月2日從[[天主教亞特蘭大總教區|亞特蘭大教區]]分出<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=XXIII |year=1956 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=750-752 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-48-1956-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-03-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305150633/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-48-1956-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-03-05 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>。亞特蘭大教區於1966年2月10日升為總教區，薩凡納教區成為其下轄教區。

